</tr>
<tr>
<td class="p-4 border border-gray-200"><strong>Vacancy Risk</strong></td>
<td class="p-4 border border-gray-200">Low (Once tenant signs)</td>
<td class="p-4 border border-gray-200">Medium (Seasonal fluctuations)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="p-4 border border-gray-200"><strong>Wear & Tear</strong></td>
<td class="p-4 border border-gray-200">High (Tenant lives 24/7)</td>
<td class="p-4 border border-gray-200">Low (Guests are out exploring)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
