<td class="p-4 border border-gray-200">3% - 4%</td>
<td class="p-4 border border-gray-200"><strong>7% - 11%</strong></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>

<h2>The "Hidden" Benefits of Airbnb</h2>

<p>Beyond just the money, short-term rental offers strategic advantages:</p>

<h3>1. Property Condition</h3>
<p>In a long-term rental, you don't see the inside of your unit for a year. The tenant could be smoking inside, keeping pets, or neglecting cleaning.
<br>In an Airbnb, the unit is <strong>professionally cleaned every 2-3 days</strong>. Minor repairs (leaky faucet, loose handle) are fixed immediately by our team, keeping the property in showroom condition.</p>

